		<title>Holiday heart: The overindulgences during festival season that put even healthy people at risk</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/holiday-heart-the-overindulgences-during-festival-season-that-put-even-healthy-people-at-risk/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Sharon Theimer]]></dc:creator>
